<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="27Jul1925"><font color="red">27 July 1925</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Harriet Weaver): we leave tomorrow for Rouen, H&ocirc;tel de la Poste. Even here I cannot escape Shaun and I added or changed about a hundred things in Anna Livia which I sent on to Miss Beach who is holding the MS &hellip; While I was returning from an excursion to S. Val&eacute;ry the idea for the last watch of Shaun came into my head. But I suppose I ought to ease off. When you return to London I shall explain why I did not send the typescript. </div>
